org.sirius.client.web

Class WebClientCoreProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sirius.client.web.core.WebCoreProxy
      • org.sirius.client.web.WebClientCoreProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Remote, WebCore

    public class WebClientCoreProxy
extends WebCoreProxy
    Contains core API for interaction with the Web applications. It's purely core and plain API which is the basis for high-level window classes library in the org.sirius.client.web.classes package.
    Author:
    Myk Kolisnyk
